n拎去問仲話要先收檢查費再報價，咁睇洗唔洗要成千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"4b079cdaf1ccee8e986e44853b42ae47958a5563","tid":125572,"uid":34165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T23:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>排線問題，重新壓可以解決，不過相信同款機型主流問題</blockquote><br />\n巴打唔係好明，你指既重新壓係指用手壓一壓個mon? <br />\n洗機解唔解決到問題？</blockquote><br />\n雖然唔知咩係重新壓<br />\n不過見你話用手壓一壓個mon覺得好好笑<br />\n幫推</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n壓過條排線呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係用手壓<br />\n<br />\nmon同老母間有排排線，你個情況應該係其中一兩個joint位甩左，有保養就拎返原廠整啦</blockquote><br />\n仆街，就係啱啱過左2年保養，一過保養就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街Asus<br />\n<br />\n拎去問仲話要先收檢查費再報價，咁睇洗唔洗要成千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n覺得礙眼你成部換啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔打機換macbook好過換其他notebook<br />\n<br />\n冇budget 買macbook，就唔整啦。ASUS整黎都哂錢，隨時屈你壞motherboard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9eb029eca6e3d3df6e7b2d0a42577f707f0dca","tid":125572,"uid":37585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T00:27:07.000Z","msg":"其實e家轉埋macbook la，同埋巴打好似90年代d 人，又用手壓mon又覺得洗機整得返個mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}